#summary Golf Markup Language Documentation: simpleType Angle90.

== Name ==

*[SAngle90 Angle90]*

  	

===  Super Types ===
{{{
double
  |
  +--Angle90 (restriction)
}}}
----
    

===  Documentation ===
        
				Angle between -90 and 90 degrees.
		
  	
===  Properties ===

  	This component is not nillable.
---- 	
        
===  Model ===

	inclusive lower bound: -90inclusive upper bound: 90.0

----
    

===  Local Usage ===

    	[CGolfClub GolfClub], [CPositionGPS PositionGPS]
----
    <xs:simpleType name="Angle90">  <xs:restriction base="xs:double">    <xs:minInclusive value="-90"/>    <xs:maxInclusive value="90.0"/>  </xs:restriction></xs:simpleType>
----
